Class AbstractLeadedComponent<T>

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractRadialComponent, AbstractSchematicLeadedSymbol
public abstract class AbstractLeadedComponent<T>
extends AbstractTransparentComponent<T>

Base class for all leaded components such as resistors or capacitors. Has two control points and draws leads between them. Also, it positions and draws the shape of the component as specified by a child class.

Author:
Branislav Stojkovic
